div.div:
Li Yan, diagnosed with a fatal disease, accidentally found his way into the strange world of Purgatory. Step by step, relying on his fighting skills, he became a powerful figure. And as he traveled through the realms of Purgatory, he was able to uncover the truth behind this world.

(Source: Tencent, translated)

"A tsundere chairwoman, a demure secretary, a black diamond of a South African princess, a unique female bodyguard, and a carrot-eating, somewhat typical, bishounen - how will these people fall in love? Whether it was fate inevitable or the heart's machinations, if you meet with the Godly Expert, you will experience a one-of-a-kind apprentice life." (Source: QQ, translated)
